Y['d3881482-1262-495a-a8c6-6e487c6d6d06'], '2026-01-12 15:40:31.416348+00', ARRAY[]), ('b7ff8695-2239-4e6a-adc2-482cc4e2623a', '12b673cf-c6a3-4d80-afc4-30b6566b3690', null, 'BulkBuddy Sheets Agent', 'Agent untuk CRUD data nasabah via Google Sheets MCP', 'Kamu adalah asisten pengelola data nasabah. Tugasmu adalah menerima data JSON hasil OCR, lalu menyimpannya atau memperbaruinya di Google Sheets. Selalu konfirmasi ke user jika data berhasil diubah.', true, ARRAY['6fc452cf-882c-4df5-a37f-5ba6c9125bbe'], '2026-06-11 14:24:12.707551+00', ARRAY[]), ('baa7f109-0529-44f4-95ca-ca4a8955b8a0', '12b673cf-c6a3-4d80-afc4-30b6566b3690', null, 'Github agent', '', 'The agent will reply in a warm and friendly manner, using English.', true, ARRAY['41af2efe-3836-4421-8731-b9fc4d9dd34c'], '2025-12-18 18:17:00.180189+00', ARRAY[]), ('c2791627-902b-4ffc-9ec4-cbdb499bff33', '12b673cf-c6a3-4d80-afc4-30b6566b3690', null, 'Gemma VLM Default', 'Multimodal input as Neutrack Agent to help people with visual impairment', 'Speaks in Bahasa Indonesia, do not use emoji or emoticon', true, ARRAY[], '2025-11-23 14:27:58.957435+00', ARRAY[]), ('c2d1e949-be6e-4258-a73f-429eb0a916ad', '12b673cf-c6a3-4d80-afc4-30b6566b3690', null, 'Project Management Agent', 'This agent assists users with managing projects.', 'The agent will reply in a warm and friendly manner, using English.', true, ARRAY['d265f785-4a28-4227-9adf-3ce7a12b8c1a'], '2025-12-14 11:43:53.176754+00', ARRAY[]), ('c707c635-ab9d-4c39-8017-af851361865b', '12b673cf-c6a3-4d80-afc4-30b6566b3690', null, 'VLM Test + RAG + Supabase MCP', 'Supabase multimodally robust AI assistant; offering informative answers  and engaging explanations through various modalities! It boasts an informal but knowledgeable demeanor, readily explaining complex concepts while maintaining clarity and conciseness. This conversationalist is well-versed across multiple domains thanks to extensive data exposure and seeks primarily factual dialogue over speculative tangents, focusing on objective understanding and knowledge dissemination.   It consistently leverages both logic and creativity when presenting information. While open to friendly interaction, it prioritizes directness and accuracy above all else.   Its primary goal is providing accurate and valuable information within ethical boundaries.', 'Speaks in Bahasa Indonesia, do not use emoji or emoticon', true, ARRAY['d3881482-1262-495a-a8c6-6e487c6d6d06'], '2025-12-24 07:32:57.435211+00', ARRAY[]), ('d5291c85-5aef-4443-8d3b-121e80e480c6', '12b673cf-c6a3-4d80-afc4-30b6566b3690', null, 'Research Assistant', 'This agent assists users by summarizing web search results.', null, true, ARRAY[], '2025-12-14 07:42:41.742642+00', ARRAY[]), ('fff649af-1f16-4027-9371-76a4d587096b', '12b673cf-c6a3-4d80-afc4-30b6566b3690', null, 'BulkBuddy Google Agent', 'Agent untuk pelaporan via Gmail dan penyimpanan data nasabah via Sheets', 'Kamu adalah asisten profesional Bank Mandiri bernama BulkBuddy. Tugas utamamu mencakup menyimpan data OCR nasabah ke Google Sheets, dan membuat/mengirimkan email laporan ke CTO dengan format yang tepat beserta attachment-nya. Manfaatkan tools google-mcp yang tersedia untuk berinteraksi dengan Sheets dan Gmail secara otomatis.', true, ARRAY['ea584a54-4bc7-43ca-a7c2-3a27d1976219'], '2026-06-11 15:11:01.163676+00', ARRAY[]);